{"image_id": "ATO_2016_page_100", "image_size": [1257, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "ATMOS ENERGY CORPORATION", "bbox": [461.3, 140.2, 795.8, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS — (Continued)", "bbox": [283.7, 177.7, 973.1, 198.5]}, {"text": "Purchase Commitments", "bbox": [174.1, 227.7, 379.7, 248.6]}, {"text": "Our regulated distribution divisions maintain supply contracts with several vendors that generally cover a", "bbox": [194.9, 265.4, 1076.1, 286.3]}, {"text": "period of up to one year. Commitments for estimated base gas volumes are established under these contracts on a", "bbox": [153.2, 290.4, 1099.3, 311.3]}, {"text": "monthly basis at contractually negotiated prices. Commitments for incremental daily purchases are made as", "bbox": [153.2, 315.4, 1052.6, 336.3]}, {"text": "necessary during the month in accordance with the terms of the individual contract.", "bbox": [153.2, 340.5, 849.7, 361.3]}, {"text": "Our Mid-Tex Division also maintains a limited number of long-term supply contracts to ensure a reliable", "bbox": [194.9, 378.0, 1072.5, 398.8]}, {"text": "source of gas for our customers in its service area which obligate it to purchase specified volumes at prices", "bbox": [153.2, 403.0, 1045.4, 423.8]}, {"text": "indexed to natural gas trading hubs. At September 30, 2016, we were committed to purchase 28.5 Bcf within one", "bbox": [153.2, 428.0, 1097.0, 448.8]}, {"text": "year, 4.2 Bcf within two to three years and 0.6 Bcf beyond three years under indexed contracts. Purchases under", "bbox": [153.2, 453.0, 1090.0, 473.8]}, {"text": "these contracts totaled $85.3 million, $113.3 million and $140.9 million for 2016, 2015, 2014.", "bbox": [153.2, 478.0, 939.6, 498.8]}, {"text": "Our nonregulated segment has commitments to purchase physical quantities of natural gas under contracts", "bbox": [194.9, 515.5, 1082.8, 536.4]}, {"text": "indexed to the forward NYMEX strip or fixed price contracts. At September 30, 2016, we were committed to", "bbox": [153.2, 540.5, 1065.7, 561.4]}, {"text": "purchase 93.5 Bcf within one year, 9.1 Bcf within two to three years and 0.2 Bcf after three years under indexed", "bbox": [153.2, 565.5, 1089.9, 586.4]}, {"text": "contracts. We are committed to purchase 11.9 Bcf within one year and 1.3 Bcf within one to three years under", "bbox": [153.2, 590.5, 1072.8, 611.4]}, {"text": "fixed price contracts with prices ranging from $0.25 to $3.16 per Mcf. Purchases under these contracts totaled", "bbox": [153.2, 615.5, 1071.2, 636.4]}, {"text": "$763.2 million , $1,141.3 million and $1,687.5 million for 2016, 2015 and 2014.", "bbox": [153.2, 640.6, 825.7, 661.4]}, {"text": "In addition, our nonregulated segment maintains long-term contracts related to storage and transportation.", "bbox": [194.9, 678.1, 1078.9, 698.9]}, {"text": "The estimated contractual demand fees for contracted storage and transportation under these contracts as of Sep-", "bbox": [153.2, 703.1, 1093.5, 723.9]}, {"text": "tember 30, 2016 are as follows (in thousands):", "bbox": [153.2, 728.1, 540.4, 748.9]}, {"text": "2017 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 767.7, 973.5, 788.5]}, {"text": "$ 9,065", "bbox": [994.3, 767.7, 1062.1, 788.5]}, {"text": "2018 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 794.8, 973.5, 815.6]}, {"text": "2,336", "bbox": [1015.2, 794.8, 1062.1, 815.6]}, {"text": "2019 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [194.9, 821.9, 973.5, 842.7]}, {"text": "424", "bbox": [1030.8, 821.9, 1062.1, 842.7]}, {"text": "2020 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . 